                                <h1>Twilio Flex Integrations</h1>
                                <p>TWILIO FLEX is a programmable contact center platform that Booking Ninjas has integrated, which can easily store and analyze client data simultaneously. By adding Twilio Flex to the Booking Ninjas platform, we’ve created an unparalleled communication experience for our customers.</p>
                                <p><a href="https://www.twilio.com/flex" target="_blank">Twilio Flex</a> is considered the most flexible cloud contact center in the world. It was a natural fit for integration as a Booking Ninjas feature because our&nbsp;<apex:outputLink value="{!URLFOR($Page.BN_Solutions)}" target="_blank">property management software</apex:outputLink> (PMS) features are designed for and marketed as the most flexible of all PMS systems in the world.</p>
                            </div>
