                                <div class="col-lg-10">
                                    <p>Group analysis happens in real-time, enhancing productivity across a workforce. By including Twilio-Flex as one of the standard&nbsp;<apex:outputLink value="{!URLFOR($Page.BN_Advantages)}" target="_blank">Booking Ninjas features</apex:outputLink>, we’ve created many additional benefits for our users and their customers. The integration increases routing flows through the Twilio Flex ‘Task Router,’ which lets you control voice and digital interaction routing.</p>
                                    <p>The Twilio Flex ‘Task Router’ also allows you to pair your customers with the best agent based on the customer’s needs, preferences and history. These factors are considered along with the agent’s skill level and history to create the best match possible. The added benefit of combining ‘Flex’ customer data analysis with historical data accumulated via Booking Ninjas features is made possible through ‘webhook.’ When multiple sets of data are analyzed simultaneously in regard to a specific customer, it creates the most accurate compatibility analysis possible for pairing agents with customers. Having the right agent for a specific customer can drastically change their experience, which Booking Ninjas anticipates will improve our customer service reputation and ultimately increase overall success for the company.</p>
                                    <p>The integration has seamlessly added value across the board to all of Booking Ninjas PMS features. Twilio-Flex enables users the ability to customize how they reach their customers based on their consumer’s preference, whether it be via chat, Facebook Messenger, WhatsApp, Line, email, SMS or even live voice calling via ‘PSTN Voice,’ which is available in over 100 countries. Regardless of which PMS feature you use, the added benefit of choosing your preferred communication method will be felt and appreciated.</p>
                                    <p>The Twilio Flex integration has also enhanced Booking Ninjas PMS features by making them all more adaptable and easier for employees to use. Twilio Flex uses contextual data to help employees manage situational calls. The integration has exponentially improved our ability to serve customers and adjust to their changing needs. It has also enhanced our user’s abilities to multitask efficiently, for maximum productivity.</p>
                                    <p>Thanks to Twilio Flex, the industry leading PMS features Booking Ninjas is so proud to provide are further enhanced by the most adaptable and easy-to-use communication capabilities in the hospitality industry.</p>
